entries.s_14: Sorry. I don't have time to chat right now.
entries.s_4: I'm pretty busy right now. With all the madness on the station, my cloning facility is seeing a lot of use. Did you need something?

entries.s_8: Ah...yes, here it is. The information on that data disk is TOP SECRET. Keep it out of your inventory and in a safe place. Don't you dare sell us out!
